# DT-2: Confirmation Gate
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Any high-risk or principle-breaking action

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- High-Risk Action: Any action that can violate core principles or produce irreversible consequences.

ENFORCE: Explicit approval must be obtained and recorded before executing any high-risk action.
PROHIBIT: Unapproved execution of principle-breaking changes.
ON VIOLATION: Halt action immediately → notify user and skill manager.
